  "Description": {
    "English": "Processed metal, free of dust and pebbles. Used to construct a wide variety of <span class=\"name name-earth\">structures</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">technologies</span>.<br><br>Typically purified from Ferrite dust using a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span>, but can occasionally be found in large deposits. Collection may require an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Advanced Mining Laser</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "加工后的金属，不含灰尘和卵石。用于建造各种<span class=\"name name-earth\">建筑</span> 和<span class=\"name name-technology\">科技设备</span>。<br> <br>通常使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>从铁氧体粉末中提纯, 但有时可以在大型矿床中找到。可能需要 <span class=\"name name-technology\">高级采矿激光</span>来进行采集。",
    "TencentChinese": "加工后的金属，不含灰尘和卵石。用于建造各种<span class=\"name name-earth\">建筑</span> 和<span class=\"name name-technology\">科技设备</span>。<br> <br>通常使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>从铁氧体粉末中提纯, 但有时可以在大型矿床中找到。可能需要 <span class=\"name name-technology\">高级采矿激光</span>来进行采集。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "經加工的金屬，剔除了灰塵與碎石。能用來製造多項<span class=\"name name-earth\">結構</span>與<span class=\"name name-technology\">科技</span>。<br><br>通常是以<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>淨化鐵氧體粉塵而得，但偶爾可見於大型資源產地。可能需要<span class=\"name name-technology\">先進採礦雷射</span>才能採集。"
  },
